MyBroadband has launched a Black Friday 2018 survey in the build-up to the shopping day. The survey asks questions about your plans for the day, including whether you will shop on Black Friday, how much you plan to spend, and what you consider a good deal. All responses to the survey are anonymous. The survey will only take 1 minute to complete, and you can win cool prizes. To enter the competition, complete the survey and say “Done” in this forum thread. The prizes up for grabs are: